      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="post-body-wrap">
    <div class="post-grid">
      <article class="post-content">
        <p class="lede-p"><strong>Yoast SEO is the most successful WordPress plugin of any kind.</strong> It is also a plugin — not a content engine, not a research tool, not a publishing service. After 30 days inside Free, Premium, Local SEO, and the Premium Plus bundle, plus interviews with 10 paying customers, here is the honest 2026 verdict, the real monthly cost, and the eight situations where Yoast is genuinely the right call.</p>

