            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>

        <p>Multi-site discounts apply at 5+ sites. The renewal price is full price (no first-year discount tricks). 30-day money-back guarantee on all paid add-ons.</p>

        <h3>The real cost of running WordPress SEO with Yoast in the stack</h3>

