            <div class="cc-row"><span>Ahrefs or Semrush (keyword research)</span><strong>$129</strong></div>
            <div class="cc-row"><span>Surfer / Frase (content scoring)</span><strong>$119</strong></div>
            <div class="cc-row"><span>Writers — articles @ $100 each</span><strong>$3,000</strong></div>
            <div class="cc-row"><span>Editor + project management</span><strong>$1,200</strong></div>
            <div class="cc-row cc-row-total"><span>What you actually spend</span><strong>$4,456 /mo</strong></div>
          </div>
