            <p>Want articles written AND published to your WordPress? Let's see if your site qualifies.</p>
            <a href="/demo/">Get my free audit →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="callout callout-warn">
          <div class="callout-label">⚠️ Yoast is a configuration tool</div>
          <p>Installing Yoast does not improve rankings. Configuring it correctly + publishing content that targets the right keywords improves rankings. The plugin is the easy 5% of SEO. The remaining 95% is research, writing, publishing, and link building.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="inline-cta dark">
          <div class="cta-copy">
            <h4>Want to know if Yoast Premium is enough for your site?</h4>
            <p>We'll audit your WordPress site and show you exactly what would generate the highest ROI — Yoast Premium, RankMath Pro, or a done-for-you content service.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="cta-action">
            <a href="/demo/" class="cta-btn-inline">Book my strategy call <span>→</span></a>
            <span class="cta-meta">30-min · No pitch</span>
