              <li>Free version covers 80% of small-site needs</li>
              <li>Premium internal linking suggestions speed up topical clusters</li>
              <li>Documentation and Yoast Academy content is excellent</li>
              <li>Customer support is human and responsive</li>
              <li>Newfold acquisition has not yet hurt the product</li>
            </ul>
