              <li>Some Premium features (redirects) are standard in RankMath Free</li>
              <li>Subtle performance overhead on older shared hosts</li>
              <li>Multi-site licensing gets expensive at scale</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="inline-cta">
          <div class="cta-copy">
            <h4>Want SEO articles written AND auto-published to your WordPress?</h4>
            <p>theStacc generates 30 SEO articles per month, optimised for your keywords, and posts them directly to your WordPress (Yoast-compatible). <strong>Try it for $1</strong>, cancel anytime.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="cta-action">
            <a href="/checkout/" class="cta-btn-inline">Start $1 trial <span>→</span></a>
            <span class="cta-meta">No annual contract</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 id="performance">Performance benchmarks — Yoast vs RankMath vs AIOSEO</h2>

        <div class="stat-grid">
          <div class="stat-card">
            <div class="stat-num">12M+</div>
            <div class="stat-lbl">Active WordPress installs</div>
          </div>
